quote.p:
Noting also with satisfaction that the Government of the Netherlands plans to
                        transfer sovereignty to the United States of Indonesia by January 1, 1950,
                        if possible, and, in any case, during the year 1950;

Conscious of its primary responsibility for the maintenance of international
                        peace and security, and in order that the rights, claims and position of the
                        parties may not be prejudiced by the use of force;
